    <item>
      <title>如果上诉失败，苹果将从手表中撤下血氧工具以避免美国禁令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/apple-to-remove-watch-blood-oxygen-app-to-avoid-ban-masimo-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苹果公司计划从其最新的智能手表中删除血氧功能——系列 9 和 Ultra 2 –如果上诉失败，可以绕过美国对这些设备的禁令。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/apple-to-remove-watch-blood-oxygen-app-to-avoid-ban-masimo-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 17:48:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普华永道英国老板表示，由于人工智能，年轻员工需要呆在办公室</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/ai-means-young-staff-should-work-in-the-office-says-pwc-uk-boss-kevin-ellis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[会计巨头普华永道的英国老板表示，初级员工应该花更多的时间在办公室，以便更快地晋升，因为人工智能将承担传统上交给年轻员工的日常任务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/ai-means-young-staff-should-work-in-the-office-says-pwc-uk-boss-kevin-ellis</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 17:45:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>人工智能和气候变化威胁着全球近一半的企业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/davos-2024-climate-change-ai-threat-are-major-concerns-for-ceos-says-pwc</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项调查显示，近一半的全球首席执行官表示，由于人工智能等技术进步的步伐和气候压力，他们的商业模式在十年内将不可行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/davos-2024-climate-change-ai-threat-are-major-concerns-for-ceos-says-pwc</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 17:45:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大众通过改变零部件供应路线避免红海中断</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/vw-avoids-red-sea-disruption-by-rerouting-auto-parts-supply</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上个月红海危机爆发后，大众汽车公司通过迅速改变船只方向，避免了特斯拉公司和沃尔沃汽车公司面临的生产困境，确保了尽管敌对行动不断升级，但零部件的稳定供应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/vw-avoids-red-sea-disruption-by-rerouting-auto-parts-supply</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 17:20:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>捷克亿万富翁被要求支付更多现金购买 Atos 部门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/czech-billionaire-faces-demand-for-bigger-check-to-buy-atos-unit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国软件公司 Atos SE 要求捷克亿万富翁 Daniel Kretinsky 支付更多现金，因为有关收购 Tech Foundations 条款的谈判仍在拖延。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/czech-billionaire-faces-demand-for-bigger-check-to-buy-atos-unit</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 15:43:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>汤森路透与人工智能公司就授权交易进行谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/thomson-reuters-in-talks-with-ai-providers-over-licensing-deals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[汤森路透公司正在与生成人工智能提供商进行谈判，以授权新闻和数据组织的内容，并可能达成类似于 Axel Springer SE 与 OpenAI 的协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/thomson-reuters-in-talks-with-ai-providers-over-licensing-deals</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 14:13:03 GMT</pubDate>
